# Frontend → Backend env. Copy to .env for local dev.
#
# Leave VITE_API_URL UNSET (or empty) to run the app in offline/local mode.
# Local mode persists leads / todos / activities in localStorage and emits the
# same domain events the real server would, so the UI works end-to-end with no
# backend running. Use this in the Lovable preview.
#
# To talk to the real Fastify server (server/) running on your VPS, set:
#   VITE_API_URL=http://82.25.105.231:4000          (HTTP only — same-origin / curl)
#   VITE_API_URL=https://api.gharpayy.com           (recommended — HTTPS via reverse proxy)
#
# NOTE: The hosted Lovable preview is served over HTTPS and browsers BLOCK
# mixed content, so a plain http:// VITE_API_URL will not work in preview.
# Put the server behind nginx + Let's Encrypt before pointing the deployed
# preview at it.
#
# VITE_API_URL=
